OL,3,CGovernment must make 'hard choices and
OL,4,Cchange course', CBI boss to say
OL,6,FThe Government must "change course"
OL,7,Fand avoid inflicting more cost
OL,8,Fpressure on UK firms at Wednesday's
OL,9,FBudget, the boss of the UK's largest
OL,10,Fbusiness group will warn.
OL,12,FCBI boss Rain Newton-Smith will tell
OL,13,Fministers and business leaders that
OL,14,Ffirms are concerned the UK could "risk
OL,15,Fgetting locked in a stop-start
OL,16,Feconomy".
OL,18,FShe is also set to encourage the
OL,19,FGovernment to make "hard choices" and
OL,20,Favoid "death by a thousand taxes".
