OL,3,CGovernment must make 'hard choices and
OL,4,Cchange course', CBI boss to say
OL,6,FMs Newton-Smith, chief executive
OL,7,Fofficer of the group, will spread the
OL,8,Fmessage in her speech at the CBI's
OL,9,Fannual conference in central London on
OL,10,FMonday, which will also see speeches
OL,11,Ffrom Business Secretary Peter Kyle and
OL,12,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch.
OL,14,FThe event comes two days before
OL,15,FChancellor Rachel Reeves will reveal
OL,16,Fthe Government's latest tax and
OL,17,Fspending plans in her autumn Budget.
