OL,3,CGovernment must make 'hard choices and
OL,4,Cchange course', CBI boss to say
OL,6,FOn Monday, the trade body boss will
OL,7,Fspecifically call for action on
OL,8,Fbusiness energy costs and the
OL,9,FEmployment Rights Bill.
OL,11,FInitial measures linked to the Bill,
OL,12,Fsuch as day one paternity leave and
OL,13,Fchanges to statutory sick leave, are
OL,14,Fdue to come into force in April next
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FFurther measures, such as banning
OL,18,Funfair zero hours contracts, are
OL,19,Fexpected to be introduced in 2027.
